TrcFtcLib.ftclib

Class FtcTensorFlow

  • java.lang.Object
    • TrcFtcLib.ftclib.FtcTensorFlow

  • public class FtcTensorFlow
extends java.lang.Object
    This class makes using TensorFlow a little easier by minimizing the number of calls to it. It only exposes the minimum things you need to set for the FTC competition. If you want to do more complex stuff, you may consider not using this and call TensorFlow directly so you can customize other stuff. This class provides methods to simplify getting detected object info from TensorFlow.
